<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="23Sep1938"><font color="red">23 September 1938</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Maurice Craig): Many thanks for the words of the song. Curiously enough I had just asked my friend, M. Mercanton of Lausanne to send it on to you. I hope the Belfast national anthem will also announce itself to me suddenly. </div>
